<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,1105,1440]" pageId="8" pageNumber="52">
Note:— 
<taxonomicName authority="sect. Gagea" box="[292,515,1376,1402]" class="Liliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Gagea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Liliales" pageId="8" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="section" section="Gagea">
<emphasis box="[292,370,1376,1401]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="52">Gagea</emphasis>
sect. 
<emphasis box="[437,515,1376,1401]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="52">Gagea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is based on the 
<typeStatus box="[702,752,1376,1402]" pageId="8" pageNumber="52">type</typeStatus>
of the genus as designated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Uphof, J. C." box="[1108,1272,1376,1402]" pageId="8" pageNumber="52" pagination="163 - 176" refId="ref10976" refString="Uphof, J. C. (1958 - 1960) A review of the genus Gagea Salisb. I-III. Plantlife 14: 124 - 132, 151 - 161; 15: 163 - 176." type="journal article" year="1958">Uphof (1958)</bibRefCitation>
. According to the ICBN (
<bibRefCitation author="McNeill, J. &amp; Barrie, F. R. &amp; Burdet, H. M. &amp; Demoulin, V. &amp; Hawksworth, D. L. &amp; Marhold, K. &amp; Nicolson, D. H. &amp; Prado, J. &amp; Silva, P. C. &amp; Skog, J. E. &amp; Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Turland, N. J." box="[279,512,1414,1440]" pageId="8" pageNumber="52" refId="ref9790" refString="McNeill, J., Barrie, F. R., Burdet, H. M., Demoulin, V., Hawksworth, D. L., Marhold, K., Nicolson, D. H., Prado, J., Silva, P. C., Skog, J. E., Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Turland, N. J. (eds.) (2006) International code of botanical nomenclature (Vienna Code). Gantner Verlag, Ruggell, Liechtenstein." type="book" year="2006">
McNeill 
<emphasis box="[386,445,1415,1440]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="52">et al.</emphasis>
2006
</bibRefCitation>
) the typification of 
<bibRefCitation author="Levichev, I. G." box="[745,938,1414,1440]" pageId="8" pageNumber="52" pagination="225 - 234" refId="ref9564" refString="Levichev, I. G. (1990) The synopsis of the genus Gagea (Liliaceae) from the western Tien-Shan. (in Russian). Botanicheskii Zhurnal 75: 225 - 234." type="journal article" year="1990">Levichev (1990)</bibRefCitation>
using 
<taxonomicName box="[1017,1108,1415,1440]" class="Liliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Gagea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Liliales" pageId="8" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lutea">
<emphasis box="[1017,1108,1415,1440]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="52">G. lutea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is thus rejected.
</paragraph>
